Ashley Roberts, 41, is not shy of showing off her phenomenal figure and today was no different. The former Pussycat Doll stunned in a see-through sheer black dress, with striped sheer sections exposing her taut abs. She kept warm with a long black wool coat stylishly draped over her shoulders, and accessorised with dark sunglasses. Ashley shared her outfit on Instagram in view of her 701,000 followers as she posted a glamorous mirror selfie and a TikTok she made with a Heart FM colleague. She captioned the snap: "Sheer me now @riversland."